title: We Gave Our Wives A Survey | Ear Biscuits Ep.294
description:
From their husband’s worst trait to the moment when they knew he was the “one” for them, the Mythical wives reveal all in this survey. Listen to R&L look at their answers for the first time and find out what their wives really think about them on this episode of Ear Biscuits!
